title: Authorizes a court to order the confidentiality of election registration records of a victim of domestic violence
summary: Authorizes the county court, or supreme court in the city of New York, to issue a court order providing for the confidentiality of election registration records of a victim of domestic violence.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the election law, in relation to authorizing registration records of victims of domestic violence to be kept confidential in certain cases
